"The user browses View 1 at the [Overview] level and examines the overall distribution of faculty across departments, segmented by appointment type. The user selects a department of interest in View 1, which filters data in View 2 (heatmap showing correlation between faculty and courses) and View 3 (box plot for faculty-to-course anomalies). Simultaneously, View 4 provides a scatter plot analysis of rank-credit relationships, with filters for department and rank."